Interface OffHeapAddressable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    OffHeapLongAddressable, OffHeapPayloadAddressable, OffHeapPayloadIntAddressable, OffHeapPayloadLongAddressable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OffHeapLongArray, OffHeapLongArrayList, OffHeapPayloadArray, OffHeapPayloadArrayList, OffHeapPayloadIntArray, OffHeapPayloadIntArrayList, OffHeapPayloadLongArray, OffHeapPayloadLongArrayList

    public interface OffHeapAddressable
    Basic interface for off-heap long-indexed collections. Required for OffHeapLongBinarySearch.
